 to confirm Google sees your mobile-friendly website.</p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 30px 0 50px;\"><a class=\"button\" style=\"padding: 10px 25px; border: none; color: #fff; background-color: #8a9d43;\" href=\"http://wptouch.s3.amazonaws.com/WPtouch%20-%20Make%20Your%20Website%20Mobile-Friendly.pdf\">Download the guide (PDF)</a></div>\n<p>Want to know more about Google&#8217;s changes? <a href=\"http://www.wptouch.com/wptouch/google-start-penalizing-non-mobile-friendly-websites/\">Read our earlier post</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:82:\"http://www.wptouch.com/tips/making-your-website-mobile-friendly-with-wptouch/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"WPtouch Pro 3.7.5: Mobile-friendly websites made even easier\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"http://www.wptouch.com/releases/3-7-5-mobile-friendly-made-easier/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"http://www.wptouch.com/releases/3-7-5-mobile-friendly-made-easier/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"