air problems like damaged hair or hair loss</p>\n</li>\n	<li>\n<p class=\"font_8\">Looking for ways to maintain your existing hair</p>\n</li>\n	<li>\n<p class=\"font_8\">Want to promote hair growth</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<b>How We Can Help You</b>\n<div id=\"WRchTxtc-yqo\" class=\"s76\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$cjpx.1.$WRchTxtc-yqo\">\n<ul class=\"font_8\">\n	<li>\n<p class=\"font_8\">Discover your hair care needs</p>\n</li>\n	<li>\n<p class=\"font_8\">Find out hair problems that you\'re facing, and provide a solution to reduce or eliminate those problems</p>\n</li>\n	<li>\n<p class=\"font_8\">Deliver a hair care solution that fits your needs, and to help you look naturally beautiful</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"WRchTxte-1chn\" class=\"s76\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$cjpx.1.$WRchTxte-1chn\"> For a consult, please contact us at:  1-877-273-6487.</div>\n<div id=\"HtmlCmpnnt0-1bm8\" class=\"s79\" data-state=\"hasContent\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$cjpx.1.$HtmlCmpnnt0-1bm8\"></div>\n<h2 class=\"font_2\">Salon Professional Suite</h2>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h2 class=\"font_2\"></h2>\n<p class=\"font_8\">Package Description: Shears Point is revolutionizing the salon and spa industry by providing exceptional online management services.</p>\n\n<h3 class=\"font_8\">Our services include:</h3>\n<p class=\"font_8\"><strong>Online Marketing &amp; Web App Integration</strong>\nThrough our site your clients will have full access to schedule in real time. Members can book appointments 24/7 and you and the client will receive email reminders of the appointment.\nDoes your salon need a website? Let Shears Point team of experts build your salon an online presence that will appeal to potential clients.</p>\n<p class=\"font_8\"><strong>Credit Card Processing/Point -of-Sale</strong>\nMembers booking online will pre-pay for service