ailable to bridge the gap between professionals and clients. From assisting with booking questions to providing directions to your locations; we are here to provide support for you and your clients.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><strong>Business Admin &amp; Reporting System</strong>\r\nBusiness administrative services cover a gambit of services from productivity for employees to client loyalty reports. We keep statistical data for your review as well as a client database for running promotions and marketing campaigns. In the future we will offer a Shears Point email address.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"> Are you ready to get started? Visit our website @ shearspoint.com or call 1-855-274-3277.</p>\r\n<a href=\"https://booknow.appointment-plus.com/3bjvgk6q/\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-248 size-medium\" src=\"http://www.leeoyote.net/heavenlyessence/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/ShearsPointClick-300x105.png\" alt=\"ShearsPointClick\" width=\"300\" height=\"105\" /></a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Services','','inherit','closed','closed','','96-revision-v1','','','2015-05-27 03:27:53','2015-05-27 03:27:53','',96,'http://www.leeoyote.net/heavenlyessence/uncategorized/96-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(265,1,'2015-05-27 03:55:54','2015-05-27 03:55:54','<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Contact Us</h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div id=\"WRchTxt6g\" class=\"s82\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$corq.1.$WRchTxt6g\">\r\n<div id=\"WRchTxt6grichTextContainer\" class=\"s82_richTextContainer s82richTextContainer\" data-reactid=\".0.$SITE_ROOT.$desktop_siteRoot.$PAGES_CONTAINER.1.1.$SITE_PAGES.$corq.1.$WRchTxt6g.0\">\r\n\r\n<span class=\"font_5\">Heavenly Essence, Inc.\r\n</span>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">Toll Free:       877.273.6487</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">Phone:           916.501.3766\r\nFax:                 916.714.0616\r\nEmail:             customerservice@heavenlyessence.net</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">find contact form an