igncenter wp-image-288\" src=\"http://www.leeoyote.net/heavenlyessence/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/SuccessBook-224x300.jpg\" alt=\"SuccessBook\" width=\"163\" height=\"219\" /></a>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h1 class=\"font_7\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Look Great, Feel Good the Healthy Way With Pure\'ity Haircare Products</strong></h1>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"font_7\"><a href=\"http://www.leeoyote.net/heavenlyessence/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/PurietyBottles-e1425670607859.jpg\"><img class=\"  wp-image-12 alignright\" src=\"http://www.leeoyote.net/heavenlyessence/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/PurietyBottles-e1425670607859.jpg\" alt=\"PurietyBottles\" width=\"319\" height=\"212\" /></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><strong>No Harmful Chemicals, Pure Natural</strong>\r\nMost hair products on the market contain chemical substances that strip hair of its natural oils. This can be a problem when trying to manage and style your hair the way you like it. But with Pure’ity hair products, that problem is minimized, as there are no harmful chemical substances that strip your hair of its natural oils. So instead of dry, frizzy hair, you receive clean, manageable hair.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><strong>Limited Fragrance, Fresh Scent</strong>\r\nMany hair products contain fragrances that causes allergic reactions like headaches, lightheaded symptoms, sneezing and more. Pure’ity hair products are mildly fragrances so that you\'ll smell only a limited mild Peppermint or Citrus scent after use. Your hair stays clean and your scalp refreshed.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><strong>Natural Ingredients, Pure Formulation\r\n</strong>Even so called natural products on the market can contain toxic ingredients (sometimes more chemicals than natural ingredients). Pure \'ity hair products are naturally formulated with the consumer in mind who wants true, pure results for their hair.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><strong>Hypoallergenic for Pure Results\r\n</strong>Our products are hypoallergenic, and in definition terms that means designed to minimize the likelihood of an allergic response, as by containing few or no potentially irritating substances. What this means for you is, not likely to cause an allergic reaction. However, that doesn\'t mean you will not experience an allergic reaction. What it does mean in reference to our products is all the natural ingredients in our products were chosen for their ability to combat allergies in hope to minimize the potential of an allergic reaction. This means you can safely use Pure \'ity hair products to obtain beautiful, healthy, and moisturized hair; and minimize your risk of experiencing an allergic reaction.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><strong>The Benefits of Using Pure’ity Hair Products\r\n</strong>In a nutshell, here is what you can expect from using Pure’ity hair products:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li class=\"font_8\">Restores the shine and luster to your hair</li>\r\n	<li class=\"font_8\">Gently cleanses hair leaving it free of residue and residual fragrance</li>\r\n	<li class=\"font_8\">De-tangles, moisturizes and leaves hair manageable</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><strong>Difference Between Peppermint and Citrus</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>Pure\'ity Peppermint shampoo</strong></span> cleanses the hair and scalp without leaving a residue. This formulation alleviates scalp irritations, while removing build up from medications, gels and other styling aids. The fragrance is minimal, so if you’re a person with fragrance sensitivities the mild scent will dissipate once rinsed. Your scalp will tingle and feel cool and fresh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>Pure\'ity Peppermint conditioner</strong></span> provides the finishing touch your hair needs to be silky smooth and lustrous. As soon as you apply it, you\'ll notice the conditioner going to work, to soothe your scalp, and moisturize your hair leaving it manageable and easy to style.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Pure\'ity Citrus shampoo</strong></span> deep cleanses your hair, while leaving a slight, fresh lemony scent. No matter the condition or texture of your hair, Pure’ity will deep cleanse to remove gels and other styling aids, leaving your hair “clean” and revitalized.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Pure\'ity Citrus conditioner</strong></span> moisturizes, de-tangles, restores luster and shine to damaged hair.</p>\r\n<p class=\"font_8\">We\'re a company that places emphasis on providing real hair care solutions that provide you with real results for your hair. If you’re looking for, healthy and safe hair care solutions, then <strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><a href=\"http://www.leeoyote.net/heavenlyessence/store/\">Click Here</a></span></strong> to visit the Pure’ity hair products page and place an order.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"font_8\"><a href=\"http://www.leeoyote.net/heavenlyessence/store/\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-223 size-full\" src=\"http://www.leeoyote.net/heavenlyessence/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/BuyNowButton.png\" alt=\"BuyNowButton\" width=\"210\" height=\"53\" /></a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-348\" src=\"http://www.leeoyote.net/heavenlyessence/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/Author.jpg\" alt=\"Author\" width=\"182\" height=\"281\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\">D</span>arlene <span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\">A</span>lexander</span> <span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">is a licensed hairstylist with 31 years of experience. The last 3 years her primary focus has been on hair replacement services. She is also Vice President of Heavenly Essence Inc, creators of Pure’ity hair products. She’s helped several women who are struggling with hair problems, and educates them on naturally promoting a